  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to BlackJack Math!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tease your brain in this number logic game where all answers are 21 (because we're talking about blackjack, right?)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swap the cards, make the math, repeat. That's all you'll need in order to complete this game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341220/extras/a18d65496297b7f9db24236e3519c503.poster.avif?t=1728907234\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341220/extras/a18d65496297b7f9db24236e3519c503.webm?t=1728907234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341220/extras/a18d65496297b7f9db24236e3519c503.mp4?t=1728907234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Handcrafted Levels</strong><br>The game comes with 50 handcrafted levels that will tease your brain.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Simple controls</strong><br>The game is played simply by swaping the cards in order to change the math result to be 21.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Relaxing music</strong><br>Originally composed music to help you focus and relax while solving the puzzles (that if you do wish, can be downloaded for <strong>free</strong> in our soundtrack page!).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341220/extras/93b0d4fad0bead345ddde4153a5a203a.webp?t=1728907234\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to BlackJack Math!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tease your brain in this number logic game where all answers are 21 (because we're talking about blackjack, right?)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swap the cards, make the math, repeat. That's all you'll need in order to complete this game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341220/extras/a18d65496297b7f9db24236e3519c503.poster.avif?t=1728907234\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341220/extras/a18d65496297b7f9db24236e3519c503.webm?t=1728907234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341220/extras/a18d65496297b7f9db24236e3519c503.mp4?t=1728907234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Handcrafted Levels</strong><br>The game comes with 50 handcrafted levels that will tease your brain.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Simple controls</strong><br>The game is played simply by swaping the cards in order to change the math result to be 21.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Relaxing music</strong><br>Originally composed music to help you focus and relax while solving the puzzles (that if you do wish, can be downloaded for <strong>free</strong> in our soundtrack page!).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341220/extras/93b0d4fad0bead345ddde4153a5a203a.webp?t=1728907234\" width=400 height=30 /></span></p>",
